<h2 style="line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">Online Bill Pay</h2>
The hospital has a patient portal that allows patients, or their authorized representatives, to pay their hospital bill online. In order to access the portal you must first be registered.<br />
&nbsp;
<div style="text-align: center;"><header3>Already registered?<br />
<a href="https://www.thrivepatientportal.com/#login" target="_blank">Online Bill Pay</a></header3></div>
<br />
<header4><header5>Follow these instructions to register the first time for online bill pay:</header5></header4>

<ol>
	<li>&nbsp;Call the main hospital number at 217-774-3961 and ask for Health Information Management (HIM) (Medical Records) at extension 1021. &nbsp;The department is open Monday through Friday, 8 a.m. to 4:30 p.m.</li>
	<li>You will be asked several questions by the HIM team in order to verify your identity.</li>
	<li>Once proper identification is established you will be asked to provide an e-mail address so a confirmation message may be sent to you in order to begin your registration process.</li>
	<li>Check your e-mail inbox or spam folder for a confirmation e-mail sent from &lsquo;donotreply@cpsi.com&rsquo;.</li>
	<li>Click the link provided in the e-mail to create a new user account.</li>
	<li>Complete the registration process. &nbsp;You will be asked to enter your name, date of birth, unique user name and password. &nbsp;Be sure to check the box at the right to verify the information you have entered is correct. &nbsp;Then click the &ldquo;register&rdquo; button at the bottom of the screen.</li>
	<li>Choose three security questions, provide the answers to the questions and then click &ldquo;submit&rdquo;.</li>
	<li>On the next page click &ldquo;Main Menu&rdquo; to begin looking at your clinical records or pay your bill.</li>
	<li>To view clinical information click on the &ldquo;View Clinical Information&rdquo; link. &nbsp;From the patient list, click on the name of the patient you are authorized to view. &nbsp;The patient&rsquo;s clinical visits will be listed chronologically. &nbsp;Next to each visit there is a link that shows the account number and the title Summary of Care. &nbsp;Click on this link to view the document for that particular visit.</li>
	<li>To pay your bill click on the &ldquo;Pay Your Bill&rdquo; link. &nbsp;Follow the on page instructions to submit a payment for the desired account.</li>
</ol>
If you have forgotten your user ID or password, please click on the portal link above and then click on the &ldquo;Forgot your user id or password&rdquo; link at the bottom of the page. &nbsp;You will be guided through the process of accessing this information. &nbsp;Please note that hospital personnel does not have access to your user IDs or passwords, so please keep these in a secure place.<br />
